version_description: Only one i found with chords for this.
This version features a simple chord version.
This is 99% accurate chords for Divinyls Casual Encounter album version. Play it with electric guitar with good gain and high volume. Certain Spotify versions cut it short at the end FYI.
This is a 99% accurate chorded version of Divinyls' Good Die Young. Play as standard on acoustic or barred on electric. Play it loud to enjoy the melodies.
R.I.P. Chrissie Amplett sticking it her life. This is a basic chorded version of Divinyls - In My Life. Played at capo 1 this should be played loud.
This is a 99% accurate simple chorded version of Divinyls' Only Lonely. Fun to play on electric. Turn it up and appreciate 80's Aussie rock.
99% accurate chorded version of Divinyls - Only You. Very fast tempo enjoyed best on an electric guitar with some good gain. Turn it up.
99% accurate Divinyls Ring Me Up chords at Capo 1. Play in time with the song and it is very enjoyable loud.
This is a version using chords from the key of F. It is easier to play and has lyrics that are more accurate.
Classic Divinyls track Sleeping Beauty. Use Capo at Fret 1. Sounds best on an acoustic guitar.

This tab represents a basic chorded version of Divinyls Take a Chance. Listen carefully to change the sound of the chords in the verses or simply strum up on the off beat. Enjoy with high gain and volume.
Based off of the Jesus Freak Album chords, but the chord placement has been improved, and much easier to read and play along with the recording.
